                  <handDesc>
                     <handNote scope="sole" script="Grantha">
                        <desc>Grantha.</desc>
                        <p source="#WinternitzKeith1905">Kṛṣna, pupil of Rāmacandra, who writes:
                           śrīrāmacandrapādābjaṣaṭpadibhṛtacetasā | Rāmāyaṇam idaṃ śrīmatkṛṣṇena
                           likhitam mudā ǁ … śrīmaty Ayoddhyānagare sabhāyāṃ siṃhāsane
                           mantragaṇābhiṣiktaḥ | Saumitrisitāhanumatsametaḥ śrīkāmacandraḥ śrīyam
                           ātanotu ǁ</p>
                     </handNote>
                  </handDesc>

